Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:12.40,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(1958,2458,\1c&HDEDDFA&\3c&H000038&\4c&H000038&)}Just like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.03,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:16.62,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're someone who will cherish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:18.29,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:23.17,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to have anything to do with someone who won't cherish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:26.88,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I'd rather be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.17,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:31.43,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappear from someone's heart again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:34.51,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If it's like that, I'd rather we had never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:44.27,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Can I stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:45.36,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:48.82,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Can you look at me alone at all times?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:49.86,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:53.87,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to let go of something important to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:24.49,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.17,0:01:26.23,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:27.69,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what it's about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:30.82,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Your...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:45.50,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:54.52,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:02.60,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:05.23,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.71,0:02:06.23,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.23,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you choose, her or me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:10.98,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going, are you, Hirono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:16.20,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me alone. Don't look at anyone other than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.54,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:19.05,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:31.42,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here. I'll be back real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:37.87,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You left after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:45.56,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:48.65,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.27,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to shoot this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:56.20,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You want to shoot this, right? Shoot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:02.24,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Just shoot it. Such an amusing scene won't happen a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.52,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:04.97,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:23.26,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:26.18,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.62,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:29.81,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Kei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.31,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Can we meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:37.21,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.15,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should be asking you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.16,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do, Hirono?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:42.86,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Planning to do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:46.52,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out with Miyamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.50,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,How is that relevant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.75,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,What about Kei-chan then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:55.01,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? Kei and I don't have that kind of relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.58,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:04:00.07,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving things half done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:03.11,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're half-assed about your studies, about your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.71,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Don't abuse others like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:07.39,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying things I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:11.19,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can beat me with your left hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.69,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,My right hand is for work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.44,bw,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're half-assed even at fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.40,bw,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.79,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You try to run away from everything like that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.44,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've never tried to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:22.84,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Taking something on without thinking about it and then dragging it along
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,is the same as running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:30.44,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you run away without trying to persuade your dad too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:33.00,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.63,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,What is Kei-chan to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:37.55,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Is she family, or a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:39.71,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Neither. Kei is Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:42.24,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said you're half-assed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:45.25,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,She cried because you didn't make yourself clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:50.68,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're making her suffer because you're running away with your indecisive attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:57.95,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, she'll follow you forever, crying like a lost child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:03.46,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one, Hirono, who can help her with her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:08.40,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:10.87,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.07,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.48,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:26.51,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:28.13,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:28.97,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.32,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not see each other anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.39,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:38.19,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's painful for me to think about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:43.64,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(\1c&HE8E8E8&\3c&H161616&\4c&H161616&)}I know I'm saying something selfish. I also know it's wrong for me to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:48.74,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,But your heart doesn't belong to me and me alone after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:50.61,bw,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:56.81,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I'll disappear from your heart again when it fills with other things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:06:00.81,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, let's break up before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:03.50,bw,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Miyako! Miyako!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:13.81,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.38,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.62,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:31.11,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:34.14,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,How was Kei-senpai's sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:34.73,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:38.56,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,She suddenly called me up last night and asked me how to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:39.96,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,How frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:40.38,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.33,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What on earth is that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:46.65,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,She suddenly began to cook. I thought it was strange, so I asked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:51.63,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,And she said boldly, "It's for Onii-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:53.64,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Plus her face was all red.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:59.38,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice, so I taught her how to make it while holding back my tears for her happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:01.06,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:04.65,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I got something in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.57,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:08.07,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,The subscription postcard to the monthly publication MIMI.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:11.93,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,This month's present to the reader is extremely valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.70,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.25,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama, are you a fan of Shindou Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:20.17,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, since his name is similar to Kei-senpai's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:21.66,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:27.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? It's a different author for "works of interest"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:31.59,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Because lately, Shindou Nagi's works haven't been interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:38.39,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow his vigor has decreased. His works used to have more sparkle to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:43.65,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, his works have been too ordinary. They're not Shindou Nagi-like anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:47.11,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you wouldn't understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.89,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:55.12,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Being half-assed at everything... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.12,bwT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:13.10,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing something and understanding it are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.51,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I know that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:21.94,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,They're all important to you, so you don't want to let go of any of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:24.05,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:27.08,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,But one day you'll have to give up on one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:31.03,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of not letting go of what's most important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:33.60,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, they're all important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:37.26,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't choose one, you'll end up losing everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:42.05,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I can't abandon something I got involved with and pretend nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:43.75,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're not abandoning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:51.05,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,They're asking you to abandon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:55.07,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:09:00.25,MainF,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:04.51,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as you live, you can't run away from pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.40,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:15.66,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Letting go of a bond that you created will cause you the same pain as having your body torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:20.40,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Can you guys bear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:23.45,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't run away even if we can't bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.28,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.13,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,You actually knew the answer from the very beginning, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:42.00,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did, I lacked the courage to understand its meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:50.50,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like... I've seen the color I've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:07.29,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.33,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.60,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot your crutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.64,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:15.77,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself before your knee recovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:17.16,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:20.97,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, thank you for the sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into Hayama and heard about it from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:30.08,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,And she told me that my manga wasn't interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:36.48,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, I'm going to quit school and devote myself to being a manga artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:41.10,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't right to do an indifferent job on it till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:44.90,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't draw something well if I'm indecisive about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:48.98,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Is that related to Miyamura-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:52.29,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's not unrelated, but it's something I thought through myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.94,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You've decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:54.96,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:59.22,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You were always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:04.41,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You decide everything on your own and proceed ahead by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:06.22,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.59,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You fulfill your dream and do what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:13.06,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You carry it through to the end, even though it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.36,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Because you've been watching out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:15.36,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:19.53,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to act cool in front of the girls who called me "Onii-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:24.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to make you two happy. That's why I started drawing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.83,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.50,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:35.58,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember? We fought while we were reading this manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:36.25,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.58,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:42.83,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,The last chapter took an unexpected turn. We were surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:48.10,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us, including Chihiro, argued about whether we liked or hated the way it ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:52.69,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You took the side of the girl who got dumped at the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:56.62,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You insisted it was her fault that she got dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:12:01.20,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't make any effort, just because she was kind of pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:04.70,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, that was already the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:09.54,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,But we didn't even realize it and were absorbed in the ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:13.00,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,That's what reality is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.08,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.79,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to have a fair ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.10,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,That ending was more realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:23.51,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,One day, it suddenly comes to an end without prior notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:29.72,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's been dreaming about it before then like an idiot is destroyed in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:31.01,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:31.81,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.27,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't end it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.25,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:41.95,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I thought our relationship would continue forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:44.56,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be with me, I'd be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:48.55,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You'd always be sloppy and need me to take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:55.36,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd always do my best to support you, and you'd support me when I was having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.69,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,We'd fight sometimes, then make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:02.50,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, our relationship as brother and sister would turn into being lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:06.35,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Before long, we'd get married and have kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:10.82,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It would... it would keep going on like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:12.79,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:17.48,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think, Onii-chan? Tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:24.03,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I thought something like that as well. I thought it would somehow turn out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:30.67,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Really? So it was just too late for me to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:34.37,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I should've admitted my feelings sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:37.04,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:40.58,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:42.91,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:47.03,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:48.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:51.55,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, since we were small.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:52.68,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:55.08,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I yearned for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:55.56,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.81,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It was my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:58.61,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:01.81,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I had... I had always loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:02.40,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:13.20,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go back. To the time when we were always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.45,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,To the time when you were with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:18.21,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,We can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:20.96,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back, Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:23.97,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're not related by blood, you're my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:26.09,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're someone important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:26.63,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:34.64,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What... it was painful for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:38.09,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:39.42,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.63,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:46.57,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll take some time, but I'll definitely be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:48.48,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.71,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,This is my last time looking at this place too, eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.99,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.48,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as before anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.72,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to turn a blind eye to what I don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:04.43,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to stop my ears against what I don't want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.88,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I've always done that, and I've survived until now that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.35,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to choose anything then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:12.55,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I gave up on that from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:15.54,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,But that person is trying his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:19.29,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be as strong as Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:21.89,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pity. I wanted to watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:26.65,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,A dream that might bring someone like me happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:30.12,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:40.66,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:41.66,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:42.64,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:43.50,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.01,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can we talk face to face?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:47.33,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,No. My determination will waver if we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:48.66,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Determination means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:50.73,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to leave this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:53.01,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'm going to a place nobody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:54.84,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:56.96,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,This is my last call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:16:00.51,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,This is my last farewell to you, who has been nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:01.52,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:06.19,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might've been testing you till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.19,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Testing means...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:10.02,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we met on Christmas night...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:13.73,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've been observing your reactions since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:17.53,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,To see if you were someone who'd cherish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:20.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't need to go as far as testing me for something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:24.20,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If I wasn't going to be cherished, I didn't want to get involved with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.69,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,And then? How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.88,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,The result of the testing. Did I fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.71,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. You got full marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:34.55,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nice person, and too good for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.55,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:38.39,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I have an eye for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:41.22,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Then why'd you say you're going to leave town?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:44.06,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be erased from your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.89,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make myself disappear while you still love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:48.13,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:50.87,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't a sound in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:51.56,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:54.40,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,My parents were always at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:57.24,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Both papa and mama kept their mouths shut at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:17:02.91,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't talk at all. They didn't even want to hear each other's voices or footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:06.75,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Their minds were full of hate for each other, and they were too busy to care about their own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:08.58,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,My name...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:09.58,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:12.42,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,They hardly ever called my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.15,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That's how little talking there was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:19.93,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how well I did in school, even if I was number one in sports, they never praised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:23.76,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I even learned how to prepare the fish recipe that papa and mama loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:26.60,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I cut myself a lot with the kitchen knife, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.43,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:35.11,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It was strange though. I didn't really need to mimic them, but I always felt breathless anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:39.78,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, they got divorced about six years ago. Frankly speaking, I felt relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:42.62,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I was free.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:48.29,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I quit that house without sound, and started going wherever I wanted to go freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:52.12,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I hoped that I'd find a home somewhere one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.00,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It was relaxing not to be involved with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:18:00.63,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't feel tired, and I didn't need to be careful to avoid being hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:03.47,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I could go anywhere, whenever I liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:07.39,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I could go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:15.37,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,But... but, being able to go anywhere meant that I didn't have a home anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:20.49,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Not having a place I wanted to go to or return to was like being all alone in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:21.88,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:25.16,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Stop babbling by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.16,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:30.25,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why didn't you tell me about this sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:32.63,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You felt lonely, didn't you? You felt pain, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.67,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,If so, you should've told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:38.52,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could tell you! If I had told you, you'd have pitied me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:42.17,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be cherished, not pitied!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.01,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, your home will be by my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:50.68,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, your family and your life by yourself will become your past. It'll be okay then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:54.23,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have a home, I'll be afraid of losing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.39,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:57.36,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:58.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:00.84,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to. I want to trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:02.03,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something you're not satisfied about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:06.36,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm horrible! You'll definitely hate me one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:07.70,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:11.09,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I knew how you and Kei-chan felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.37,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I couldn't win against Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:18.61,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to stay by your side so desperately that I held onto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:21.32,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,And I knew you were suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:25.72,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the worst. I only think about myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:29.27,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think about my problems. You're just fine as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.39,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's more like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:34.23,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've found the answer to my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.90,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:39.90,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:42.73,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappear anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:45.57,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here, so I don't want to be ignored!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:48.41,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always looking at you. How could you disappear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.24,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:54.08,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I want my cooking to be eaten while it's still warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:55.91,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.75,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I want someone to praise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:02.12,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say you're amazing if you do well in school!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:03.98,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll scold you if you do something bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:05.42,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, I'll eat your cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:09.70,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how disgraceful it is, I want to cling to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.93,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You can just do what you want to do! I'll accept it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:14.97,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:18.60,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:04.57,bw,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(1830,2122,\1c&HDEDDFA&\3c&H000038&\4c&H000038&)}I... love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.40,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:12.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:15.33,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've gone to all the public telephones in Otowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.83,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.16,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako.
